<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-243290-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-243290-2')">2</a>. To accommodate six teams, the number of monthly front page features will be doubled.</div>
</div>

