<p><strong>I'm interested! How do I sign up to be a flight officer?</strong></p>
<p>Simply create a New Post/post a new comment (don't use &quot;reply&quot;) in this thread stating:</p>
<ul>
<li>which Flight you are interested in (Flight 1, 2, or either)</li>
<li>a quick sentence about why you would like to be part of the mentoring process</li>
<li>optional: the name of the commander(s) you would like to work with, and one sentence why.</li>
</ul>
<p>If a commander is interested in mentoring you, they will respond to your post.</p>
<p><strong>I'm interested&#8230; but I think I want to work on my critique skills first/I didn't get picked this month. What can I do?</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Get the basics down! Start here: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-9804362/so-you-want-to-be-a-concept-reviewer">http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-9804362/so-you-want-to-be-a-concept-reviewer</a></li>
<li>Read! The Guide Hub &quot;critter resources&quot; section: <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/guide-hub#toc4">http://www.scp-wiki.net/guide-hub#toc4</a> has some resources you can use to practice different kinds of critique, as well as improving your reviewer skills overall.</li>
<li>Practice! There are always plenty of authors looking for feedback in the forums.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>I'm interested in being a commander/mentor! How do I put my name forward for consideration?</strong></p>
<p>Simply send a wikidot message to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609478134" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;">Zyn</a></span> stating your interest, and noting which of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9804362/so-you-want-to-be-a-concept-reviewer#post-4183926">four criteria for giving greenlights</a> you fulfill.</p>

